# Licensing — Agentic Software Operations

This bundle is **split-licensed** — the same model as its two component products
(Atlassian Companion and Product Ops 2.0) — so the open methods can be freely
adopted while the author's commercialization path is preserved:

- **Skills & documentation** (`**/SKILL.md`, `**/references/`, `spec/`, `*.md`) —
  Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International (**CC-BY-4.0**). Free to read,
  cite, and implement, with attribution. See `LICENSE-SPEC`.

- **Code & tooling** (`*.py`, `build.sh`, `.claude-plugin/`, the assembled plugin) —
  Functional Source License 1.1 with an MIT future license (**FSL-1.1-MIT**). Free
  to use, modify, and redistribute for any Permitted Purpose, but **not** to
  repackage-and-resell as a competing product. Converts to the MIT License two
  years after release. See `LICENSE-CODE`.

The bundle composes content from both component products, each of which carries
this same split license; the composition is licensed consistently.

Authored by Fred Chong Rutherford. The **Agentic Software Operations** product line
comprises this bundle plus Atlassian Companion and Product Ops 2.0.
